{
  "text": "The results for the related approaches were taken from the respective papers, except for ESA, which was taken from [CITATION_1] , where it is calculated via the public ESA REST endpoint [CITATION_2] . All results are collected in table 5. We can see that our approach, using inverse predicate object frequency weights, outperforms the state-of-the-art approaches, as well as the embeddings generated by RDF2Vec.",
